        <div class="contentfontsize">
            Villa Madonna offers a wide variety of Fine Arts programs in order to inspire, support, and celebrate the uniqueness of EVERY child. We are blessed with an incredibly 
            talented faculty who insipre amazing results in the students at every grade level. 
