    <div id="contentwrapper">
        <p class="lesserheader">Theater & Drama<p>
        <div class="row">
            <div class="col-md-6 col-sm-12 col-xs-12">
                <div class="contentfontsize">
                    Students in every grade participate in full scale musical productions, under the direction of Roxanna Harst, who was  herself, a professional ballerina! Students in Grades 4 
                    and above can audition for the main cast, or main chorus in the productions. Students in Grades 7-8 can choose Drama as an elective class during the year. Younger students 
                    participate in the annual Christmas Spectacular, a musical celebrating the birth of Jesus..
                </div>
            </div>
