            </div>
            <div class="col-md-6 col-sm-12 col-xs-12">
                <div class="contentfontsize p-3">
                    Students wishing to learn the BEHIND THE SCENES aspect of theater can join the Backstage Crew. Students learn to run a sound board, light board, 
            spotlights, and prop & stage management. All performances and productions are run entirely by students!
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
